  "theorem_seqs": [],
  "raw_answer": "设PM＝x，PN＝y，∵AB∥CD，MN∥AB，∴AB∥MN∥CD，∴△CDP∽△ABP，∵AB＝2，△PDC与△PAB的面积比为1：4，∴CD＝1，∵AB∥MN∥CD，∴△DMP∽△DAB，△CPN∽△CAB，∴\\frac{PM}{AB}=\\frac{PD}{DB}，\\frac{PN}{AB}=\\frac{CP}{AC}，∵\\frac{PD}{PB}=\\frac{PC}{PA}=0.5，∴\\frac{PD}{DB}=\\frac{CP}{AC}=\\frac{1}{3}，∴\\frac{x}{2}=\\frac{1}{3}，\\frac{y}{2}=\\frac{1}{3}，解得：x＝y＝\\frac{2}{3}，∴MN＝x+y＝\\frac{4}{3}．故选：C．"
